WEBVTT

00:00:00.355 --> 00:00:00.766
yo.

00:00:01.030 --> 00:00:04.370
un ir hot gevolt epes dertseyln nokh vegn oktober, bite.

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:07.550
oktober iz geven, oktober khoydesh ober UNK...

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:08.870
dos iz geven fir in fertsik.

00:00:09.418 --> 00:00:09.726
yo.

00:00:10.823 --> 00:00:13.292
in oktober ze'mir nokh dort geven in

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:14.056
Birkenoy.

00:00:13.658 --> 00:00:15.181
Birkenoy.

00:00:15.806 --> 00:00:18.560
hitst ze'mir aroysgegangen yedn in der fri.

00:00:19.566 --> 00:00:22.332
un far undz iz geganen fun fuftsik mentshn,

00:00:23.621 --> 00:00:28.572
eltere mentshn, oykh aroys komando in shtrayfedike kleyder.

00:00:29.797 --> 00:00:31.395
yedn in der fri far undz.

00:00:32.324 --> 00:00:37.280
un mayn tsvey khavertes zenen k- krank gevorn,

00:00:37.756 --> 00:00:43.283
hobn zey nisht geganen in REVIR, zenen zey geganen hobn zey nisht demolts mit undz nisht aroysgekumen.

00:00:44.391 --> 00:00:52.689
un ven undz geyen mir shoyn aheym, ovnt, undz zeen mir nisht di fuftsik mentshn.

00:00:54.635 --> 00:00:59.405
un vi azoy ze'mir geganen, efsher a ts- tsvey kilometer.

00:00:59.621 --> 00:01:04.743
s'iz geven a vald, ober nisht a a groyse vald, aza kleyne vald.

00:01:05.081 --> 00:01:13.189
un undz zeen mir ven kum mir az dey fuftsik mentshn tsien dort epes mentshn.

00:01:13.270 --> 00:01:14.023
veysn zi?

00:01:14.567 --> 00:01:18.891
un far undz shrayt der mit hunt, mit boln hint,

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:23.148
di tsvey soldat, S.S., hobn geshrign,

00:01:23.243 --> 00:01:27.401
"LOS, LOS, SCHNELLER, SCHNELLER!" az undz zoln mir nisht zen gornisht.

00:01:27.464 --> 00:01:30.648
dort iz geshtanen dray groyse mashines

00:01:30.648 --> 00:01:34.216
un veysn zi, in SONDERKOMMANDO,

00:01:34.581 --> 00:01:39.875
ver hot gearbet in krematorye zenen, hobn zey gehat birgelekh, veysn zi,

00:01:40.054 --> 00:01:43.223
birgelekh sheyn ongeton, do iz geven di vinkl.

00:01:43.770 --> 00:01:48.400
un zeen mir zenen fun zey sakh toyte oyfn mashin shoyn oyfge-

00:01:48.594 --> 00:01:50.778
in sh- a sakh daytshe soldatn.

00:01:51.635 --> 00:01:58.012
vos ken dort zayn? un zey tsien di di partizanen zenen geven,

00:01:58.175 --> 00:02:00.635
un tsien dort di toyte mentshn,

00:02:01.189 --> 00:02:02.869
vos ken dos zayn?

00:02:03.216 --> 00:02:06.554
hobn mir nisht gevust, geyen mir arayn di khaverte zogn.

00:02:06.851 --> 00:02:08.309
ober dos hobn mir gevust,

00:02:08.391 --> 00:02:11.675
koydem hot men gebrengt fuftsik, dos,

00:02:11.810 --> 00:02:16.835
partizanen hot men oykh mitn gaz im tsu brenen.

00:02:17.121 --> 00:02:20.766
di andere tog hot men gebrengt hundert, oykh geharget.

00:02:21.027 --> 00:02:25.395
un dey tog hot men gebrengt hundert tsvontsik partizanen.

00:02:26.581 --> 00:02:29.918
un vi azoy hot men zey ge- gebrengt,

00:02:30.596 --> 00:02:35.292
hobn zey ongehoybn tsu shrayen, "mentshn! ver iz do in lager?

00:02:35.491 --> 00:02:41.288
kumts mit undz! kumts, hitst iz di tsayt loyfn mir avek!"

00:02:41.371 --> 00:02:45.123
un hobn zey genumen a,

00:02:45.123 --> 00:02:49.157
vos hobn zey gehat, a sherl ober vos UNK hobn zey di drot

00:02:49.228 --> 00:02:52.649
tsu tseshnaydn un der, di eyne iz dort geblibn,

00:02:52.709 --> 00:02:55.385
ober di iberike zenen avekgelofn.

00:02:55.438 --> 00:02:57.122
hobn zey geshist!

00:02:57.122 --> 00:02:59.877
hobn zey ge- di S.S.n geharget!

00:03:01.063 --> 00:03:03.840
hern zi, un far a tsvey sho,

00:03:04.378 --> 00:03:10.012
s'iz geven an S.S. velkhe yedn tog iz er gekumen kukn vi azoy undz arbetn mir.

00:03:10.366 --> 00:03:12.092
er iz geven a fayner mentsh, zeyer.

00:03:13.189 --> 00:03:15.600
un zeen mir di kop iz oyfn boym,

00:03:16.583 --> 00:03:22.400
un di iberike er iz hintn, ligt er on kop. vi azoy iz gekumen di kop oyfn boym?

00:03:22.892 --> 00:03:23.943
yo, OPSHE.

00:03:24.389 --> 00:03:25.612
geyen mir arayn.

00:03:26.298 --> 00:03:28.873
un hot men gezogt vos hot zikh pasirt.

00:03:28.989 --> 00:03:32.675
sakh mentshn zenen aroys fun lager, zenen far...

00:03:32.914 --> 00:03:36.222
un sakh partizanen zenen oykh avekgelofn,

00:03:36.222 --> 00:03:37.509
ober sakh hot men geharget.

00:03:38.006 --> 00:03:41.651
i di SONDERKOMMANDOS, ale zenen avekgelofn.

00:03:41.796 --> 00:03:45.509
un azoy vi azoy hot men zey aropgebeytn yedn dray monat.

00:03:46.001 --> 00:03:47.293
az, yo.

00:03:47.438 --> 00:03:51.016
nu, un nokh dem, in november di ershte,

00:03:51.671 --> 00:03:58.962
hot men undz aroysgetrogn in lager tsu di shtantsyon,

00:03:59.030 --> 00:04:01.276
in di vagones arayngeleygt,

00:04:01.402 --> 00:04:03.813
ze'mir geganen in RAVENSBRUÌˆK.

00:04:03.948 --> 00:04:06.860
ober dray tog un dray nakht,

00:04:07.082 --> 00:04:11.750
vayl s'iz geven milkhome, zenen geganen, veysn zi.

00:04:11.885 --> 00:04:15.559
un ven ze'mir geganen in in komando in Birkenoy,

00:04:15.781 --> 00:04:18.880
s'iz geforn di ban, un oyf di mentshn

00:04:18.963 --> 00:04:24.248
velkhe iz shoyn geven pasirt, hobn zey azoy geyoyket, azoy s'iz geven a UNK.

00:04:24.450 --> 00:04:27.237
un hot men undz avekgetrogn in RAVENSBRUK.

00:04:27.806 --> 00:04:33.120
RAVENSBRUÌˆK ze'mir geven in karantin dray vokhn.

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:36.901
nokh dem hot men dort vayter oysgeveylt.

00:04:37.614 --> 00:04:45.269
hot men toyznt tsvey hundert mentshn avekgetrogn in MALCHOW, in MUNITION fabrik.

00:04:46.545 --> 00:04:53.882
ze'mir geganen dray kilometer ahin un dray kilometer tsurik.

00:04:54.161 --> 00:04:58.289
y- eyn vokh hobn mir gearbet bay tog, eyn vokh bay nakht,

00:04:59.057 --> 00:05:04.446
un di esn, dort hobn mir zikh shoyn geshpirt,

00:05:04.753 --> 00:05:10.892
yeder hot gehat eygene bet, ekster di kots, un ekster teler,

00:05:10.892 --> 00:05:12.307
veysn zi?

00:05:13.523 --> 00:05:20.617
s'iz beser geven, ober di arbet iz shverer geven. un nokh dos,

00:05:20.617 --> 00:05:23.205
ze'mir arayngeganen in munitsye fabrik

00:05:23.205 --> 00:05:29.235
hobn mir, keyner hot hot nisht gezogt in vald az dort iz do munitsyon fabrik.

00:05:29.294 --> 00:05:35.705
dos iz geven in bunkers, in oyfn bunkers, oyvn iz geven di boymer ayngezet in vald.

00:05:35.705 --> 00:05:39.529
se iz zeyer sheyne SZERPENTIN veg iz es geven.

00:05:40.205 --> 00:05:43.088
un hobn mir gearbet.

00:05:43.088 --> 00:05:47.764
un s'iz gekumen CHRISTMAS, far zey, un der nayer yor,

00:05:48.176 --> 00:05:50.852
vos hobn zey far undz gegen esn?

00:05:50.882 --> 00:05:54.411
royte kroyt un vaser, opgekokhte.

00:05:55.418 --> 00:05:57.783
un hobn mir gegesn.

00:05:58.183 --> 00:06:00.195
s'iz gut geven vayl s'iz geven varem.

00:06:00.753 --> 00:06:06.662
ikh hob genumen efsher a fir finef mol un bin ikh gegan un betn nokh nokh

00:06:06.987 --> 00:06:10.423
un bin ikh krank gevorn.

00:06:10.467 --> 00:06:12.428
bin ikh krank gevorn,

00:06:12.428 --> 00:06:20.285
hob ikh gelign in revir mit groyse temperatura a dray vokhn, ikh hob gemeynt az ikh kum shoyn nisht fun dort aroys.

00:06:20.480 --> 00:06:24.805
nokh dray vokhn bin ikh s'iz mir shoyn beser gevorn,

00:06:25.025 --> 00:06:27.571
bin ikh tsurikgeganen arbetn.

00:06:28.480 --> 00:06:33.129
ober ikh hob gearbet bay dos pres.

00:06:33.246 --> 00:06:35.740
veysn zi, PRESH, vu hot men...

00:06:35.922 --> 00:06:42.272
s'iz geven aza ayzn, hot men gekent opge- onkhapn, un tsvelef koyl iz in dem arayn.

00:06:42.272 --> 00:06:46.324
un s'iz geven a kleyne KOMNATkele.

00:06:46.324 --> 00:06:52.584
dort hobn di meydlekh gevegt dey pulver, yo.

00:06:53.012 --> 00:06:55.662
un ikh bin, ikh hob gearbet bay pres.

00:06:56.389 --> 00:07:03.116
un nokh dem ven bin ikh tsurik fun shpitol, bin ikh zeyer shvakh geven, hot men mikh ahin arayngeleygt.

00:07:03.909 --> 00:07:07.883
un di TOILET iz geven vayt dort in vald.

00:07:08.194 --> 00:07:09.233
un ikh,

00:07:09.233 --> 00:07:11.038
hot men gebroykht betn

00:07:11.038 --> 00:07:13.987
"froy zenen bite, ken ikh oystretn?"

00:07:14.363 --> 00:07:15.181
"yo."

00:07:15.545 --> 00:07:19.714
ober az ikh bin geven in shpitol un ikh hob gebroykht mer mol.

00:07:19.883 --> 00:07:22.597
hot zi mikh nisht gelozt shoyn.

00:07:22.636 --> 00:07:24.935
zi hot gezogt s'iz genug geven, vos?

00:07:24.935 --> 00:07:27.311
yede sho vestu geyn?

00:07:27.870 --> 00:07:32.623
un vos zol ikh tun ikh broykh zeyer aroysgeyn?

00:07:32.805 --> 00:07:34.467
zi iz avek.

00:07:34.506 --> 00:07:39.029
un lebn bunker, vu hobn mir gearbet iz geven aza grub,

00:07:39.064 --> 00:07:41.943
un dort iz geven aza ayzn, veysn zi?

00:07:42.194 --> 00:07:43.714
az di fis opvishn.

00:07:44.064 --> 00:07:46.259
zi, ikh hob gemeynt az zi iz avek.

00:07:46.558 --> 00:07:50.662
un ikh hob mir dort aropgezetst oykh, makh PEE-PEE.

00:07:50.948 --> 00:07:54.831
vi azoy ikh gey arayn in bunker, zi kumt arayn.

00:07:55.233 --> 00:07:59.233
koydem hot zi mir gegen mitn shtivl in boykh,

00:08:00.285 --> 00:08:05.012
her zi, ikh hob nokh hitst oykh di grizhe, hob ikh bakumen a SHEVER,	

00:08:05.012 --> 00:08:06.168
nokh haynt oykh.

00:08:06.168 --> 00:08:10.454
un me ken mir nisht, eyn dokter vil nisht operirn vayl ikh hob alergye.

00:08:10.454 --> 00:08:17.493
un nokh dem hot zi mikh gepatsht, fun eyn vinkl tsun andere.

00:08:17.831 --> 00:08:19.155
hot zi geshlogn!

00:08:19.155 --> 00:08:21.402
un nokh dem hot zi gezogt,

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:27.363
"ven undz geyen mir aheym, do zolst geyn, do fornt.

00:08:28.298 --> 00:08:30.629
vestu bakumen nokh dort oykh."

00:08:30.688 --> 00:08:31.974
hot zi gezogt.

00:08:32.012 --> 00:08:35.103
vos zol ikh tun, bin ikh gegan in fornt.

00:08:36.116 --> 00:08:38.714
hob ikh geveynt a gantsn veg.

00:08:38.727 --> 00:08:41.545
un nokh dem ven ze'mir arayn in lager,

00:08:41.623 --> 00:08:46.922
ikh shtey dort, un zi iz avek, yeder iz avek un ikh shtey dort.

00:08:46.922 --> 00:08:51.168
un zogt far mir ver iz dort bay di tir,

00:08:51.168 --> 00:08:52.610
"vos shteystu do?

00:08:52.610 --> 00:08:53.935
gey aheym."

00:08:53.935 --> 00:08:59.338
zog ikh, "ikh gey nisht vayl di oyfzeerin hot gezogt zol ikh do vartn zi."

00:08:59.363 --> 00:09:04.051
"neyn. zi hot shoyn far mir gezogt zol ikh dikh araynshikn."

00:09:04.995 --> 00:09:07.714
un azoy hob ikh di krankeyt.

00:09:08.028 --> 00:09:14.118
un nokh dem iz geven hot men ge-

00:09:14.316 --> 00:09:20.425
di SAMALYOTS, di bombes, di bunkern zenen azoy geganen.

00:09:20.758 --> 00:09:22.132
in arbet.

00:09:22.240 --> 00:09:29.698
un eyn shabes mitog, dos iz geven shoyn in april khoydesh,

00:09:29.979 --> 00:09:37.137
hot men undz ge-, shoyn aheym, in lager, aheym.

00:09:37.814 --> 00:09:42.531
in di oyfzeerins, s'iz toyznt tsvey hundert, eyner hot gearbet

00:09:42.582 --> 00:09:45.004
in S.K. un eyn in

00:09:45.180 --> 00:09:48.295
di UNK S.K. un UNK M.P.

00:09:48.295 --> 00:09:51.639
tsvey munitsyon frab- fabrik iz dort geven.

00:09:51.639 --> 00:09:54.918
un s'iz gekumen a groyse MASAYID,

00:09:55.016 --> 00:09:56.704
mit kroyt.

00:09:57.749 --> 00:10:02.503
un di oyfzeerin shrayen, "LOS, LOS, FARFLUCHTE JUDEN, LOS!"

00:10:02.698 --> 00:10:03.714
zoln mir loyfn.

00:10:03.839 --> 00:10:05.728
vos meynen zey, ver hot getoygt?

00:10:06.044 --> 00:10:09.573
hobn zey oyfgekrikht oyfn mashin,

00:10:09.573 --> 00:10:12.558
un eyn heyfele kroyt iz nisht geblibn.

00:10:12.617 --> 00:10:13.683
oyfn mashin.

00:10:13.683 --> 00:10:16.941
yeder, hobn mir geshtupt in zikh, hobn mir gegesn.

00:10:17.044 --> 00:10:21.117
un di oyfzeerin hot gezogt, "nu ver vet hobn kroyt?

00:10:21.161 --> 00:10:23.519
ver trogt arayn in kl- kroyt,

00:10:23.610 --> 00:10:27.653
der vet a gantse nakht in droysn zayn."

00:10:27.653 --> 00:10:31.584
hobn mir gevolt oyfesn, ze'mir geven oysgehungert,

00:10:31.701 --> 00:10:34.000
ober hobn mir nisht gekent azoy fil oyfesn.

00:10:34.038 --> 00:10:35.857
aher hobn mir geshtupt, aher.

00:10:35.961 --> 00:10:42.000
ober ze'mir arayngeganen, hot zi nisht gezogt gornisht a vort nisht.

00:10:42.025 --> 00:10:46.727
un fun dey tog ze'mir shoyn nisht geganen arbetn.

00:10:46.831 --> 00:10:56.051
ober di Royte Kreyts hot gebrengt far undz, ende april,

00:10:56.727 --> 00:11:01.142
PASILKES, finef kilo.

00:11:01.155 --> 00:11:04.610
un keyner hot dos nisht gevolt ibernemen.

00:11:04.779 --> 00:11:11.922
s'iz geven dort an anglishe yidishe froy, oykh heftling, zi iz shoyn lang dort,

00:11:11.974 --> 00:11:20.259
un s'iz geven dray meydlekh fun Rumenye, hobn zey geheysn Tshik. Tshik.

00:11:20.961 --> 00:11:23.168
un zey hobn gearbet in kikh.

00:11:23.207 --> 00:11:31.194
un di anglishe froy, un di meydlekh hobn untergeshribn az zey veln far undz oysteyln

00:11:31.194 --> 00:11:35.415
vifl heftlingen, toyznt tsvey hundert, far undz.

00:11:36.350 --> 00:11:43.480
ober ven shoyn in april, fun fun Oyshvits,

00:11:43.480 --> 00:11:48.343
ven Oyshvits evakuirt, iz gekumen ahin tsen toyznt meydlekh.

00:11:49.395 --> 00:11:55.669
far tsen toyznt hobn zey azoy fil esn gegen vi demolts far toyznt tsvey hundert.

00:11:56.206 --> 00:11:56.960
shteln zi for.

00:11:57.932 --> 00:12:02.218
hobn mir gegesn di groz, di groz hobn mir shoyn gegesn.

00:12:03.269 --> 00:12:04.663
ze'mir geven azoy hungerik.

00:12:04.926 --> 00:12:10.583
un ven shoyn s'iz gekumen di SAMALYOTN hot men

00:12:10.649 --> 00:12:17.189
zey hobn aropge-, di S.S. aropgenumen di hit, az zol nisht zen az zey zenen S.S.n.

00:12:17.245 --> 00:12:20.515
hot men gegebn far finef mentshn a POSILKE.

00:12:20.611 --> 00:12:22.076
far finef mentshn.

00:12:22.192 --> 00:12:25.944
ober demolts shoyn gekumen arayn kranke,

00:12:25.973 --> 00:12:29.753
ver veys ken zayn mayn tatiko iz oykh dort geven.

00:12:29.811 --> 00:12:34.199
vayl zey hobn gegen far yedern a gantse, far dem iz...

00:12:34.199 --> 00:12:39.821
un hot men undz aroysgetribn shoyn zoln mir geyn.

00:12:40.207 --> 00:12:42.126
vos vil ikh aykh zogn,

00:12:42.145 --> 00:12:46.466
dey tsen toyznt meydlekh zenen gekumen fun

00:12:46.466 --> 00:12:48.741
Birkenoy, fun Oyshvits,

00:12:48.741 --> 00:12:51.345
un dey dray Rumenishe meydlekh,

00:12:51.355 --> 00:12:54.248
un zey hobn gebrengt mit zikh gold,

00:12:54.258 --> 00:12:58.202
vayl Oyshvits hot evakuirt, un dortn iz geven, veysn zi, ekster

00:12:58.221 --> 00:13:00.237
di shikh iz, zi veysn, di gold...

00:13:00.237 --> 00:13:02.329
un s'iz geven ver hot genumen.

00:13:02.387 --> 00:13:09.331
un a teler SOUP hobn zey farkoyft far di meydlekh far a a ringl, far a tshepetshke.

00:13:09.331 --> 00:13:11.858
dey dray Rumenishe yidishe meydlekh.

00:13:12.253 --> 00:13:13.690
shteln zikh for.

00:13:14.664 --> 00:13:22.340
un nokh dem ze'mir aroys oyfn gas, iz gerunen a vaser, ze'mir aroyfgegan, ho'mir z- hobn mir zikh opgevashn.

00:13:22.369 --> 00:13:26.178
un hobn mir gevart, vern mir fray.

00:13:26.468 --> 00:13:32.977
ze'mir geganen oyf a a puste berg, nor eyn daytsh hot gehat dort.

00:13:32.997 --> 00:13:35.813
vi a MOSHAV, veysn zi? kuen, ales.

00:13:37.057 --> 00:13:40.239
un ze'mir azoy opgeshvakht.

00:13:40.239 --> 00:13:42.033
hobn mir gezitsn dort.

00:13:42.351 --> 00:13:48.523
hobn mir gevartn, i veln mir fray vern, i veln mir toyt zayn.

00:13:48.523 --> 00:13:52.930
un eyn mol hern mir az dray shist men, dray.

00:13:52.940 --> 00:13:54.367
dray mol.

00:13:54.367 --> 00:13:55.621
ikh ze.

00:13:55.669 --> 00:13:58.427
un dos iz di amerikanishe.

00:13:58.475 --> 00:14:00.578
finef soldatn oyf a JEEP.

00:14:01.687 --> 00:14:05.650
un ikh zog meydlekh ze'mir fray, ze'mir fray!

00:14:05.699 --> 00:14:07.166
ze'mir fray gevorn.

00:14:07.434 --> 00:14:09.238
ze'mir fray gevorn,

00:14:09.354 --> 00:14:15.699
vos zoln mir tun dort? hobn mir geganen tsu di BAL-HABAYIT, ho'mir geganvet KARTOSHKN.

00:14:15.699 --> 00:14:17.589
oyfn tsvey tsigl hobn mir...

00:14:17.859 --> 00:14:24.504
un s'iz geven dort an alter yid, hot er opge-dost a a beheyme.

00:14:24.504 --> 00:14:27.754
un dort, d- hot zi, hobn zey dort...

00:14:27.783 --> 00:14:32.614
un undz ho'mir gegesn. un ale hobn mir bakumen SHILSHUL.

00:14:32.749 --> 00:14:34.004
fregst nisht.

00:14:34.469 --> 00:14:38.526
un nokh dem, undz geyen mir ergets aropleygn zikh.

00:14:39.646 --> 00:14:46.469
geyen mir, un dort zeen mir di anglishe, di rusishe, di amerikanishe soldatn.

00:14:46.823 --> 00:14:48.435
un me shist!

00:14:48.618 --> 00:14:50.732
dort hot zikh geendikt di milkhome,

00:14:51.372 --> 00:14:54.850
un undz ze'mir arayngefaln tsu di rusishe.

00:14:55.292 --> 00:15:01.200
un azoy hot men undz avekgetrogn in Prentsloy.

00:15:02.926 --> 00:15:09.451
un dort zenen geven di sakh fun Italye, fun Belgye, fun Frankraykh, fun H-

00:15:09.578 --> 00:15:15.406
UNK, di holandishe meydlekh hot men take avekgetrogn in in SIBERIA.

00:15:15.783 --> 00:15:26.023
hot men zey nisht UNK. un azoy ze'mir undz, oysgeputst fun di ale ale zenen aheymge-

00:15:26.096 --> 00:15:30.462
di italishe, fun di italishe hot zeyer a sakh geshtorbn dort.

00:15:31.215 --> 00:15:37.924
un, hot men nokh dem di rusn, s'iz gekumen a rusishe ofitsir, a yidishe,

00:15:38.182 --> 00:15:42.193
nokh di rumenishe meydlekh. un undz hobn mir gebetn zol er undz oykh,

00:15:42.193 --> 00:15:44.526
vos vet zayn do mit undz?

00:15:44.952 --> 00:15:48.672
zakarpatishe, ze'mir tetevirt, vos vil er dort?

00:15:48.810 --> 00:15:50.304
di hoypt shoyn.

00:15:50.838 --> 00:15:54.595
azoy vi do iz tsirke, veysn zey dort, iz geven a rusishe.

00:15:54.855 --> 00:15:58.338
er iz geganen, hot er geredt, hot er gezogt, "zayts ruik,

00:15:58.516 --> 00:16:01.316
vet kumen rusishe soldatn,

00:16:01.781 --> 00:16:05.036
in mashines," un hot men undz aroyfgeleygt in di mashines,

00:16:05.085 --> 00:16:09.270
un getrogn, un getrogn, un getrogn!

00:16:11.675 --> 00:16:16.899
hobn mir gezen nor vald, un der erd, un sakh ferd, gepeygerte.

00:16:17.957 --> 00:16:24.190
nokh dem, ikh veys nisht dos iz Kiev geven, s'iz geven a groyse brik.

00:16:24.289 --> 00:16:26.763
un untern brik iz gerunen di vaser.

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:36.027
hot men undz dort shoyn ibergegen un arayngeleygt oyfn oyfgemakhte vagones, oyfn koyln.

00:16:36.260 --> 00:16:38.616
un di shney iz gefaln.

00:16:38.739 --> 00:16:42.452
un undz ze'mir nisht geven azoy ongeton tsugegreyt.

00:16:42.684 --> 00:16:45.671
ze'mir ongekumen in Vilvo.

00:16:47.137 --> 00:16:53.054
dort iz geven a vagon shoyn nisht oysgevorfene.

00:16:53.109 --> 00:16:55.205
in dem iz geven shtroy.

00:16:55.479 --> 00:16:58.146
un undz ze'mir ahin arayngegangen,

00:16:58.205 --> 00:17:00.520
ze'mir ale layzik gevorn.

00:17:00.575 --> 00:17:03.095
vayl ken zayn dort zenen oykh geven gefangene.

00:17:03.857 --> 00:17:06.775
un di meydlekh velkhe hot gekent rusish,

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:11.392
vayl ver hot gekent hutsulish, veysn zi, Karpat.

00:17:11.428 --> 00:17:17.000
zenen arayn dort bay shtantsyon, tsu di direktor, az

00:17:17.202 --> 00:17:21.298
un undz zeen mir dort iz geven a tsvontsik, finef un tsvontsik mener,

00:17:21.508 --> 00:17:25.526
ver zenen geven nisht in lager, in Ukraine.

00:17:25.771 --> 00:17:27.824
ROBOTSYE BATALYON.

00:17:27.982 --> 00:17:31.122
un dort zenen zey arayn in eynem,

00:17:31.210 --> 00:17:34.368
un nokh tsvey vokhn hobn zey gegebn far undz...

00:17:35.035 --> 00:17:39.684
s'iz geven sakh vagones, far undz ekstere vagon

00:17:39.771 --> 00:17:43.526
un azoy ze'mir aheymgegangen.

00:17:44.052 --> 00:17:49.456
un ikh hob fun Vilvo a gantse veg geveynt.

00:17:49.456 --> 00:17:53.754
ikh hob geshpirt az mayn bruder

00:17:55.350 --> 00:17:58.157
ikh hob nisht, epes, dos harts hot mir gezogt...

00:17:58.438 --> 00:18:06.807
vi ikh gey arop bay di shtantsyon, tomed zenen geven in droysn mentshn hobn gevart yedn tog az mir kumen.

00:18:07.315 --> 00:18:11.701
zogt men dayn bruder iz geven in der heym, tsvey vokhn iz er avekgeganen.

00:18:11.824 --> 00:18:14.122
er iz in Tshekhoslovakye.

00:18:16.087 --> 00:18:20.982
er iz geven in Tshekhoslovakye un dey, mayn feter velkhe iz do in bild,

00:18:21.140 --> 00:18:26.561
vayl er hot ge- geven in, tshekhishe LEGYE.

00:18:28.105 --> 00:18:38.315
un vos, er hot geshribn a briv aheym az zol a bakante, a goy, mikh iberfirn.

00:18:38.315 --> 00:18:46.403
se vet kumen a yingl, a yungerman, un er hot shoyn oysgetsolt, un zol ikh mir gornisht trogn vayl ikh,

00:18:46.491 --> 00:18:50.947
er hot ba- tsurik- tsurikgekumen mayn bruder, mayn zakhn.

00:18:51.771 --> 00:19:00.070
un, ikh hob geveynt ikh hob keynem nisht, "vuhin zol ikh geyn? vuhin zol ikh geyn?"

00:19:00.666 --> 00:19:03.175
zogt mayn khavertes, "kum mit undz."

00:19:03.912 --> 00:19:06.421
vayl eynem iz aheymgekumen di bruder.

00:19:07.859 --> 00:19:12.070
dort, ovnt gey ikh zikh, zog ikh, "ah! ikh gey aheym!"

00:19:12.929 --> 00:19:17.473
ikh vil zen ver voynt in undzere shtub, a shokher voynt dort.

00:19:17.736 --> 00:19:21.386
un ge- hot, men gegen far mir a plats dort aropzetsn.

00:19:21.771 --> 00:19:27.623
ikh bin geganen, un mayn shokhnte zogt az mayn tokhter voynt dort hintn.

00:19:28.147 --> 00:19:32.661
un fornt iz gevoynt a rusishe ofitsir mit dray kinder mitn vayb.

00:19:33.341 --> 00:19:38.786
un dey, mayn shokhn's tokh- iz nisht geven in der heym, bin ikh ahingeganen tsurik, m- tsu di meydlekh,

00:19:38.999 --> 00:19:43.499
un far togs bin ikh geganen ahin.

00:19:43.499 --> 00:19:45.770
in undzere shtub.

00:19:46.166 --> 00:19:53.916
zi hot shoyn mikh opgebodn, un hot zi gekokht far mir. ober ikh hob nisht gekent dort lebn.

00:19:54.270 --> 00:19:59.989
in undzere shtub, vu bin ikh geganen iberol hob ikh gezen mayne eltern, mayn shvesters...

00:20:02.395 --> 00:20:08.333
un nokh detsember, yanuar, februar,

00:20:08.687 --> 00:20:14.312
ho'mir g-, ze'mir geven, koydem hob ikh gevoynt bayn a goy.

00:20:14.604 --> 00:20:20.910
UNK LEMISHPACHA, zey hobn gevoynt, di bruder hot gevoynt bayn undz hintn in hoyf.

00:20:21.395 --> 00:20:26.520
un nokh dem in marts in ershtn bin ikh geganen vayter in tsuker fabrik arbetn.

00:20:27.229 --> 00:20:32.687
un bin, ikh avek hobn mir gevoynt tsvelef meydlekh un a yingl.

00:20:32.749 --> 00:20:38.374
a yingl fun drayts- draytsn yor iz arayngekumen, fun Oyshvits.

00:20:38.541 --> 00:20:40.166
un nokh dem,

00:20:40.208 --> 00:20:45.291
in dey yor, in zeks un fertsiker yor hob ikh khasene gehat.

00:20:45.812 --> 00:20:47.749
gornisht ho'mir nisht gehat.

00:20:47.979 --> 00:20:52.923
mayn man hot gehat di shvester, der bruder, ober ikh keynem nisht.

00:20:52.923 --> 00:20:56.963
hob ikh gevust der bruder iz fun Tshekhoslovakye,

00:20:57.041 --> 00:21:00.187
avek ken Italye iz er geven anderthalbn yor,

00:21:00.187 --> 00:21:02.562
un nokh dem in Tsiprus,

00:21:02.604 --> 00:21:04.687
iz er gekumen aher,

00:21:04.833 --> 00:21:09.020
er iz geven an ofitsir, er iz gegan untern vaser.

00:21:09.062 --> 00:21:11.354
do tsvontsik yor hot er ge-...

00:21:12.729 --> 00:21:18.395
un azoy hob ikh gehat dray kinder, un mayne kinder hobn tomed gefregt,

00:21:18.541 --> 00:21:23.354
"mamiko, far vos hobn mir nisht nisht babi nisht zeydi?"

00:21:24.687 --> 00:21:29.208
un nokh dem hob ikh far zey ales fartseylt far vos.

00:21:29.270 --> 00:21:31.354
un vu, un ven.

00:21:32.187 --> 00:21:38.499
un nokh dem az mayn bruder iz do geven hot er tomed undz gerufn, "kumts aher, kumts aher,"

00:21:38.541 --> 00:21:40.958
un ze'mir gekumen aher.

00:21:41.041 --> 00:21:44.249
di mitlste, velkhe eyniklekh zenen do,

00:21:44.354 --> 00:21:46.520
ober di tsvey zin zenen,

00:21:46.666 --> 00:21:49.515
di eltere iz avek mit tsvey kinder,

00:21:49.645 --> 00:21:54.083
un fir iz shoyn dort geboyrn, un mayn zun dey David,

00:21:54.416 --> 00:21:59.541
hot gearbet do in CHEVRA CHASHMAL, iz er avek koydem UNK,

00:21:59.729 --> 00:22:03.916
iz er aheymgekumen, nokh dem di andere yor iz er gegan nokh a mol,

00:22:04.041 --> 00:22:07.187
iz er dort geblibn. hot er dort khasene gehat.

00:22:07.187 --> 00:22:09.999
hot er a yingele un tsvey meydele.

00:22:09.999 --> 00:22:14.921
hot er gelebt in LOS ANGELES, un hitst lebt er in KANSAS CITY,

00:22:14.960 --> 00:22:21.708
un di eltere iz, iz er DATI, un er voynt in NEW JERSEY.

00:22:21.708 --> 00:22:24.562
oyf english LAKEWOOD, LAKEWOOD.

00:22:26.284 --> 00:22:30.717
ikh hob aykh gevolt, oyb ir kent mir a bisl dertseyln,

00:22:30.717 --> 00:22:34.554
ir hot khasene gehat, ir hot mir gezogt ir hot gehat kinder,

00:22:34.554 --> 00:22:38.744
der- dertseylt a bisl dos lebn unter di sovyetishe regirung.

00:22:38.744 --> 00:22:41.014
vi ir hot zikh geleb-, ayer man hot gearbet,

00:22:38.837 --> 00:22:39.669
di sovyetishe...

00:22:41.014 --> 00:22:44.041
er hot gehat a gute arbet, vi hot zikh gelebt dortn?

00:22:41.045 --> 00:22:43.287
er hot gearbet, yo.

00:22:43.770 --> 00:22:48.041
zol ikh zogn di emes, s'iz shver geven dos lebn.

00:22:48.041 --> 00:22:51.708
azoy lang vi lang di kinder zenen kleyn geven.

00:22:51.708 --> 00:22:58.270
ober ven hobn zey shoyn oysgelernt di shule, mayn eltere zun hot gearbet,

00:22:58.270 --> 00:23:04.937
di velkher iz do, er hot gearbet mit mayn man in MYASOKOMBINAT.

00:23:05.562 --> 00:23:10.187
vos zol ikh aykh zogn, hobn mir nisht ge- hobn mir nisht gelebt shlekht.

00:23:10.187 --> 00:23:11.876
ze'mir nisht geven raykh.

00:23:11.916 --> 00:23:17.520
di yidn s'iz geven yidn velkhe hobn zeyer g- gut gelebt.

00:23:17.645 --> 00:23:21.145
ober nokh dem zenen zey gezitsn,

00:23:21.208 --> 00:23:24.645
finef un tsvontsik yor, tsvontsik yor, fuftsn yor.

00:23:25.318 --> 00:23:29.183
antisemitizm, hot men dort gefilt a bisl far di komunistishe tsayt?

00:23:29.166 --> 00:23:33.562
vos zol ikh aykh zogn, zol ikh zogn di emes?

00:23:31.950 --> 00:23:32.667
yo, dem emes.

00:23:33.749 --> 00:23:39.999
az dort, di goyim, gute goyim beser geven vi do di yidn.

00:23:42.437 --> 00:23:46.499
ikh zog di emes, ikh zog mit emes.

00:23:46.193 --> 00:23:48.735
iz spetsyel antisemitizm nisht geven.

00:23:47.727 --> 00:23:54.166
s'iz s'iz geven shoyn, ven ho- hobn mir ongehoybn, ven di mentshn hobn ongehoybn shoyn kumen,

00:23:54.333 --> 00:23:55.979
in YISRAYEL,

00:23:56.012 --> 00:23:59.833
un ze'mir geshtanen in OCHERED, nokh broyt nokh

00:23:59.937 --> 00:24:05.270
hobn zey gezogt, "vos shteystu do? gey shoyn in Palestine!"

00:24:06.749 --> 00:24:07.541
yo.

00:24:07.519 --> 00:24:11.222
ikh farshtey az, ven ir hot detsidirt

00:24:11.222 --> 00:24:14.330
tsu kumen do keyn Yisroel tsum bruder zikh fareynikn

00:24:14.118 --> 00:24:16.495
nokh zibn in tsvontsik yor.

00:24:14.330 --> 00:24:18.438
iz aykh nisht gegangen laykht, men hot aykh bald nisht aroysgelozt, neyn?

00:24:18.249 --> 00:24:24.937
neyn, vayl mayn, dey zun velkhe iz do, er hot ge- gesluzhet bay di raketn.

00:24:24.999 --> 00:24:30.104
az ir vilt bilder makhn, do iz do di tsvey z- groyse zin, rusishe soldatn do.

00:24:30.104 --> 00:24:31.916
in fortsimer az z-...

00:24:31.993 --> 00:24:33.406
nu, shpeter redn mit zey.

00:24:32.837 --> 00:24:33.300
yo.

00:24:33.802 --> 00:24:41.999
un ale tsvey iz geven dort in RUSKA ARMIYE, un ven di kleyne hot geendikt di elef KLASE,

00:24:42.041 --> 00:24:44.749
hot er geganen arbetn, un,

00:24:44.749 --> 00:24:50.479
ikh hob dort gemakht az zol er nisht geyn in TSAVA, vayl hobn mir shoyn arayngegen di papirn.

00:24:50.520 --> 00:24:57.541
un hobn mir gebroykht vartn finef yor zol aropgeyn mayn man tsvey groyse zun hot ge-

00:24:57.583 --> 00:24:59.624
geven in rusishe ARMIYE.

00:24:59.916 --> 00:25:00.541
yo.

00:25:00.583 --> 00:25:05.354
ober ze'mir geganen tsu zey, s'iz geven di yontev PERVOE may, un

00:25:05.395 --> 00:25:08.770
veysn zi, di OKTOBERSKY, ze'mir geganen tsu zey.

00:25:08.770 --> 00:25:15.109
s'iz zeyer shver geven s'iz, z- dort iz, azoy gehaltn di soldatn, nisht azoy vi do.

00:25:16.749 --> 00:25:23.309
yetst in in dray in zibetsikstn hot men aykh erloybt ts- aroystsuforn.

00:25:23.309 --> 00:25:24.803
in dray in zibetsikstn.

00:25:23.333 --> 00:25:29.062
yo, hobn mir arayngegebn di dokumentn un tsvey mol hobn mir bakumen OTKAZ.

00:25:29.062 --> 00:25:31.645
tsvey mol hot men aropgezogt.

00:25:31.729 --> 00:25:34.583
un nokh dem hobn mir bakumen.

00:25:35.291 --> 00:25:37.020
un zi gleybn,

00:25:37.020 --> 00:25:43.874
ze'mir avek in Uzhhorod nokh di papirn, un nokh dem hot men gebroykht, dos hot shoyn mayn zun avekgegangen in Moskove.

00:25:44.812 --> 00:25:50.558
un mayn zun, dey velkher iz do, iz shoyn geven di tsvey eynikl.

00:25:50.687 --> 00:25:57.666
nebekh, er hot azoy ibergelebt, er, er hot nisht gegleybt az im vet men a- aroyslozn vayl er iz geSLUZHET in

00:25:57.666 --> 00:26:00.041
FEODOSIYA, bay di raketishe.

00:26:00.458 --> 00:26:06.562
un, ruft men undz arayn in Berger Nikolay,

00:26:06.562 --> 00:26:08.312
ikh bin geganen,

00:26:08.458 --> 00:26:12.020
Bernatovitsh Berger Frida Yakubovitsh,

00:26:12.062 --> 00:26:17.666
I Berger Bernat, mayn kind, mayn zun der elterer, un Berger DAVID.

00:26:17.687 --> 00:26:19.416
un nokh dem,

00:26:19.416 --> 00:26:22.604
s'iz shoyn geven di TIK, veysn zi azoy.

00:26:22.645 --> 00:26:27.999
un mayn zun zitst dort nebekh, hot er azoy moyre gehat az im vet men nisht lozn.

00:26:28.020 --> 00:26:28.983
nokh dem zogt men,

00:26:29.124 --> 00:26:35.354
"BERGER YAKOB NIKOLAYOVICH,

00:26:35.354 --> 00:26:38.854
I BERGER EDITH MOROVICH,

00:26:38.854 --> 00:26:41.458
I BERGER ROBERT,"

00:26:41.874 --> 00:26:51.208
di ershte eynikl, un di tsveyte hot nokh dem geboyrn, veysn zi, un zayn iz nisht geven dort.

00:26:51.208 --> 00:26:53.729
un zog ikh, "ikh hob nokh an eynikl."

00:26:53.791 --> 00:27:02.812
"vifl alt," zog ikh, "punkt a yor." "yoy, shoyn loyfts aheym un makht bilder un brengt tsurik."

00:27:02.812 --> 00:27:04.749
vayl azoy hot men nisht avek.

00:27:04.833 --> 00:27:06.479
dort iz geven

00:27:06.479 --> 00:27:11.208
SOFKO, er iz geven di NACHALNIK MILITSYA koydem in BEREGOVO.

00:27:11.208 --> 00:27:15.749
un nokh dem iz geven a krumer, Lengel hot er geheysn.

00:27:15.749 --> 00:27:19.048
zenen geven hutsuln, veysn zi, fun UNK...

00:27:18.088 --> 00:27:19.737
fun di berger.

00:27:19.666 --> 00:27:26.312
yo, un hobn zey genumen di TIK, un "NIKOLAY!

00:27:26.312 --> 00:27:28.770
dos iz undzere khaver!"

00:27:28.770 --> 00:27:32.041
ge- dos iz undzer, afile hobn zey geveynt,

00:27:32.286 --> 00:27:35.612
hobn zey gegen di hent, un hobn zey gezogt,

00:27:35.729 --> 00:27:42.145
di SOFKO, "ikh meyn az ikh vel nokh bay dir esn khale un gefilte fish."

00:27:42.687 --> 00:27:47.499
un hobn zey gevuntshn ales guts, un hobn zey gezogt, "shrayb unter, du broykhst shoyn nisht..."

00:27:47.499 --> 00:27:55.874
mayn zun iz aheym gekumen, shoyn gemakht fun di kleyne, un ze'mir do.

00:27:55.874 --> 00:27:59.874
bin ikh gekumen mit di dray zin, hob ikh gefreyt ze'mir in eynem.

00:27:59.874 --> 00:28:02.062
un do ze'mir tsu UNK.

00:28:02.691 --> 00:28:07.070
nu, ir zent ongekumen in dray in zibetsikstn, ir hot zikh getrofn mit ayer bruder do.

00:28:04.720 --> 00:28:05.799
yo.

00:28:07.499 --> 00:28:12.895
keyner hot men nisht arayngelozt do, in AEROPORT.

00:28:12.895 --> 00:28:14.416
nor im.

00:28:14.416 --> 00:28:15.979
fregn zi nisht.

00:28:16.041 --> 00:28:18.229
nokh zibn un tsvontsik yor,

00:28:18.729 --> 00:28:22.958
un fun, zeks kinder nor tsvey ze'mir geblibn.

00:28:25.416 --> 00:28:28.166
azoy iz es dos lebn,

00:28:28.374 --> 00:28:34.015
ikh vil nokh a bisl lebn. ikh vil nokh mayn eyniklekh di groyse unter di khupe firn

00:28:34.020 --> 00:28:35.000
ober...

00:28:35.148 --> 00:28:38.742
yetst endikn mir di tsveyte kasete

00:28:37.887 --> 00:28:38.514
yo, un nokh-...

00:28:38.742 --> 00:28:42.688
un shpeter vel ikh aykh nokh fregn etlekhe frages, vegn di mishpokhe.

00:28:40.585 --> 00:28:42.831
gut, gut, gut gut.
